    In Tom Clancy&#039;s Rainbow Six: Lockdown,  you  lead  Team  Rainbow,  the
    world&#039;s most elite counter-terrorist unit, as  they  are  called  into
    action and unfamiliar  territory  to  battle  a  bioterrorist  threat.
    Stakes escalate as they are personally targeted by an  evil  terrorist
    organization. Used to protecting the lives  of  others,  Team  Rainbow
    must now embark on a mission to fight and save some of their own.
